HEADWORD: Septi-
<hw>Sep"ti-</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <ety>[L. <ets>septem</ets> seven.]</ety>
<def>A combining form meaning <xex>seven</xex>; <as>as,
<ex>septi</ex>folious, seven-leaved; <ex>septi</ex>-lateral,
seven-sided</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

